publisher			Mastertronic							
publish_time	 2014年3月5日		
desc_long							评测						“a marvellously well designed and air-punchingly triumphant video game”8/10 – Eurogamer“10 Second Ninja is fast-paced and highly-addicting with a great sense of humor from the very start.”9.3 – Indie Gaming Mag“it’s bloody brilliant”5/5 – The Indie Mine												关于这款游戏							Ninjas are cool, this is an established fact of the universe. Nazi Robots from space are not cool, they are the complete opposite of cool, and Robot Hitler is out to get you, the world's first ninja.  You have 10 seconds to destroy all Nazi Robots in your vicinity. IT. IS. ON.Become the ultimate Ninja and  take down Robot Hitler’s automated autocracy in this blisteringly fast platformer. Ready, Steady, Ninja! FeaturesBlitz through 40 challenging levels!Fight again and again to get the best time possible and a glorious three star rating!Break your controller or keyboard out of anger!Battle your friends down to the millisecond on the leaderboardsProve you know how to play games and collect all 30 achievementsWarning: This game contains flashing images. It is advised that you do not play if you suffer from photosensitive epilepsy.						
